- **Claim:** Within the healthy snacks market, products with claims such as gluten-free, low-fat, sugar-free, and others are gaining traction among health-conscious consumers. These claims help in communicating the health benefits and suitability of the snacks to individuals with specific dietary requirements or preferences.

